Flask-Defer Changelog
=====================

Version 1.1.0
-------------

:Released: 11-29-2016

:Changes:
  Public API is the same, except now we only attach functions to the request context


Version 1.0.1
-------------

:Released: 11-28-2016

:Changes:
  Execute tasks immediately if we are outside of a request context


Version 1.0.0
